<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Salud Pública Argentina</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --verde: #1a6b4a;
    --verde-claro: #e6f4ed;
    --verde-medio: #2e9b6e;
    --azul: #1a4b8c;
    --azul-claro: #e8f0fb;
    --celeste: #2979d4;
    --naranja: #d45a1a;
    --naranja-claro: #fdf0e8;
    --amarillo: #c97c00;
    --amarillo-claro: #fef8e6;
    --gris-oscuro: #1c1c1e;
    --gris: #4a4a4f;
    --gris-medio: #8a8a8e;
    --gris-claro: #f2f2f4;
    --borde: #d8d8dc;
    --blanco: #ffffff;
    --rojo: #c0392b;
    --rojo-claro: #fdecea;
    --font-title: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;
    --font-body: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
    --radius: 10px;
    --shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    color: var(--gris-oscuro);
    background: var(--gris-claro);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  /* NAV */
  nav {
    background: var(--verde);
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }
  .nav-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    height: 60px;
  }
  .nav-logo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
  }
  .nav-logo .flag {
    width: 32px;
    height: 22px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border-radius: 3px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .nav-logo .flag span:nth-child(1) { background: #74acdf; flex: 1; }
  .nav-logo .flag span:nth-child(2) { background: white; flex: 1; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
  .nav-logo .flag span:nth-child(2)::after {
    content: '☀';
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #F9A01B;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .nav-logo .flag span:nth-child(3) { background: #74acdf; flex: 1; }
  .nav-logo strong {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    list-style: none;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: background 0.15s;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: white; }
  .hamburger {
    display: none;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 5px;
    padding: 4px;
  }
  .hamburger span {
    display: block;
    width: 24px;
    height: 2px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--verde) 0%, #0f5038 60%, #0a3d2b 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem 3.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.15;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .hero p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin: 0 auto 2rem;
  }
  .hero-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  .pill {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    color: white;
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .hero-ctas {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: white;
    color: var(--verde);
    border: none;
    padding: 12px 22px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    transition: transform 0.12s, box-shadow 0.12s;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); }
  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: white;
    border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.55);
    padding: 12px 22px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: none;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }
  .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.12); }

  /* URGENCIA BANNER */
  .urgencia-banner {
    background: var(--rojo);
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .urgencia-banner .num {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--font-title);
  }

  /* SECCIONES */
  .section {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    font-size: 1.7rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gris-oscuro);
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }
  .section-subtitle {
    color: var(--gris-medio);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .section-divider {
    width: 48px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--verde-medio);
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  /* CARDS GRID */
  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; }
  .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 1.25rem; }
  .grid-4 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }

  .card {
    background: var(--blanco);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.4rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border: 1px solid var(--borde);
  }
  .card-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    color: var(--gris-oscuro);
  }
  .card p {
    font-size: 0.87rem;
    color: var(--gris);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .card a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    margin-top: 0.8rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--celeste);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .card a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* COLORES ICONOS */
  .ic-verde { background: var(--verde-claro); }
  .ic-azul { background: var(--azul-claro); }
  .ic-naranja { background: var(--naranja-claro); }
  .ic-amarillo { background: var(--amarillo-claro); }
  .ic-rojo { background: var(--rojo-claro); }

  /* HOSPITALES */
  .hosp-section { background: white; }
  .hosp-tabs {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .tab-btn {
    background: var(--gris-claro);
    border: 1px solid var(--borde);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    font-size: 0.84rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--gris);
    transition: all 0.15s;
  }
  .tab-btn.active, .tab-btn:hover {
    background: var(--verde);
    color: white;
    border-color: var(--verde);
  }
  .hosp-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
  .hosp-card {
    background: var(--gris-claro);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--verde-medio);
  }
  .hosp-card h4 {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gris-oscuro);
    margin-bottom: 3px;
  }
  .hosp-card .hosp-especialidad {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: var(--verde);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .hosp-card p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--gris); }
  .hosp-card .hosp-link {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--celeste);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-top: 5px;
  }
  .tab-panel { display: none; }
  .tab-panel.active { display: block; }

  /* VACUNAS */
  .vacuna-table-wrap { overflow-x: auto; }
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.87rem;
  }
  thead th {
    background: var(--verde);
    color: white;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }
  tbody tr { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borde); }
  tbody tr:nth-child(even) { background: var(--gris-claro); }
  tbody td { padding: 9px 14px; color: var(--gris-oscuro); }
  .badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  .badge-verde { background: var(--verde-claro); color: var(--verde); }
  .badge-azul { background: var(--azul-claro); color: var(--azul); }
  .badge-naranja { background: var(--naranja-claro); color: var(--naranja); }

  /* DERECHOS */
  .derechos-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
  .derecho-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--borde);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .derecho-num {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--verde);
    color: white;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .derecho-item h4 { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .derecho-item p { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--gris); }

  /* PROGRAMAS */
  .prog-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.2rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    border: 1px solid var(--borde);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .prog-icon {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .prog-card h4 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .prog-card p { font-size: 0.83rem; color: var(--gris); line-height: 1.5; }
  .prog-card a {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--celeste);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  /* CONTACTOS */
  .contacto-hero {
    background: var(--azul);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .contacto-hero h2 { font-family: var(--font-title); font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .contacto-hero p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); max-width: 380px; }
  .tel-big {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .tel-label { font-size: 0.78rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

  .contacto-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; }
  .contacto-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--borde);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .contacto-card .cnum {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-family: var(--font-title);
    color: var(--verde);
    line-height: 1;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .contacto-card h4 { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .contacto-card p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--gris); }

  /* SECCIÓN ALTERNAS */
  .bg-white-section { background: white; }
  .bg-verde-section { background: var(--verde-claro); }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer {
    background: var(--gris-oscuro);
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    text-align: center;
  }
  footer strong { color: white; }
  footer a { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-decoration: none; }
  footer a:hover { color: white; }

  /* BUSCADOR */
  .search-bar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }
  .search-bar input {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--borde);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    outline: none;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }
  .search-bar input:focus { border-color: var(--verde-medio); }
  .search-bar button {
    background: var(--verde);
    color: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  #search-results {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    border: 1px solid var(--borde);
    padding: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    display: none;
  }
  #search-results li { padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gris-claro); cursor: pointer; color: var(--celeste); }
  #search-results li:hover { color: var(--azul); }
  #search-results li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  /* MAPA ILUSTRATIVO */
  .mapa-info {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
  .mapa-region {
    background: white;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--celeste);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
  }
  .mapa-region h4 { font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .mapa-region p { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--gris); }

  /* ACCORDION */
  .accordion { border: 1px solid var(--borde); border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; }
  .acc-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--borde); }
  .acc-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .acc-btn {
    width: 100%;
    background: white;
    border: none;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
    text-align: left;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    color: var(--gris-oscuro);
    transition: background 0.12s;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
  }
  .acc-btn:hover { background: var(--gris-claro); }
  .acc-btn .arrow { transition: transform 0.2s; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--gris-medio); }
  .acc-btn.open .arrow { transform: rotate(180deg); }
  .acc-content {
    display: none;
    padding: 1rem 1.2rem 1.2rem;
    background: var(--gris-claro);
    font-size: 0.87rem;
    color: var(--gris);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .acc-content.open { display: block; }
  .acc-content ul { padding-left: 1.2rem; }
  .acc-content ul li { margin-bottom: 4px; }

  /* MOBILE */
  @media (max-width: 680px) {
    .nav-links { display: none; flex-direction: column; position: absolute; top: 60px; left: 0; right: 0; background: var(--verde); padding: 1rem; gap: 4px; }
    .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
    .nav-links a { padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 0.9rem; }
    .hamburger { display: flex; }
    .hero { padding: 2.5rem 1.2rem 2rem; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .contacto-hero { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .tel-big { font-size: 2.2rem; }
    .section { padding: 2rem 1.2rem; }
    .urgencia-banner { font-size: 0.85rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 400px) {
    .hero h1 { font-size: 1.5rem; }
    .grid-4 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAVEGACIÓN -->
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a class="nav-logo" href="#">
      <div class="flag"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
      <strong>Salud Pública Argentina</strong>
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <li><a href="#atencion">Atención Gratuita</a></li>
      <li><a href="#hospitales">Hospitales</a></li>
      <li><a href="#vacunas">Vacunas</a></li>
      <li><a href="#programas">Programas</a></li>
      <li><a href="#derechos">Tus Derechos</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contactos">Emergencias</a></li>
    </ul>
    <button class="hamburger" id="hamburger" aria-label="Menú">
      <span></span><span></span><span></span>
    </button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- BANNER EMERGENCIAS -->
<div class="urgencia-banner">
  <span>🚨 Emergencias:</span>
  <span class="num">107</span>
  <span>SAME Buenos Aires •</span>
  <span class="num">911</span>
  <span>Policía / Emergencias •</span>
  <span class="num">0800-999-3425</span>
  <span>Línea de Salud Mental</span>
</div>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <p class="hero-eyebrow">Sistema de salud público · 100% gratuito · Para todos</p>
  <h1>Accedé al sistema de salud público argentino sin costo</h1>
  <p>Todo lo que necesitás saber para atenderte en hospitales, centros de salud y programas estatales, sin obra social ni prepaga.</p>
  <div class="hero-pills">
    <span class="pill">🏥 Hospitales públicos</span>
    <span class="pill">💉 27 vacunas gratuitas</span>
    <span class="pill">👶 Maternidad gratuita</span>
    <span class="pill">💊 Medicamentos</span>
    <span class="pill">🦷 Salud dental</span>
    <span class="pill">🧠 Salud mental</span>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-ctas">
    <a href="#hospitales" class="btn-primary">📍 Buscar hospital</a>
    <a href="#contactos" class="btn-secondary">📞 Números de emergencia</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CÓMO FUNCIONA -->
<div class="bg-white-section">
<section class="section" id="atencion">
  <div class="section-divider"></div>
  <h2 class="section-title">¿Cómo funciona la salud pública?</h2>
  <p class="section-subtitle">Todos los ciudadanos y residentes tienen derecho a atenderse en hospitales públicos de forma gratuita, independientemente de si tienen o no obra social.</p>

  <div class="grid-4" style="margin-bottom:2rem;">
    <div class="card" style="border-top:3px solid var(--verde);">
      <div class="card-icon ic-verde">🪪</div>
      <h3>Solo necesitás tu DNI</h3>
      <p>No se puede negar atención a nadie. Con tu DNI podés acceder a cualquier hospital público del país.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="border-top:3px solid var(--celeste);">
